title: Sri Lankan Roast Eggplant Curry with Garlic-Peanut Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: This vibrant eggplant curry has flavour bursting in every bite! The garlic and peanut rice is packed with
nuttiness, balanced against the roast veggies and Sri Lankan-style spices, we reckon it’s a sure winner at the
dinner table.

